reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is EXACTLY what my NUC needed.
reviews.reviewText: I don't know where my old power adapter went to - I know I didn't throw it out (I never throw out any technology, which makes it easy to lose a power adapter in a closet full of old power adapters). Since I couldn't find it, and wanted to see if the NUC (NUC 1) was still practical, I ordered this. Then I found my other NUC (NUC 2), with its power adapter, and discovered that IT IS still practical. When Amazon delivered the other power adapter I fired up NUC 1, removed personal data, then wiped it and added Fedora - sold it on ebay. Made about 50% of my original 2017 purchase. Not bad.
